"tid":971894,"uid":150730,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-07T12:36:55.000Z","msg":"係外國住左十幾年<br />\n學得最快(講&amp;聽) 果陣係有個鬼仔fd 坐隔離討論下chem/phy/maths<br />\n反而英文堂無乜點學過野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n玩英文game 係一個好開始<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你做任務睇guide 都好多生字可以學<br />\n岩岩玩果陣好多字都要查<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5106f19865a7143a5554750f7b2db632f15b73e6","tid":971894,"uid":200686,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-07T13:22:05.000Z","msg":"你去到外國就同啲鬼妹講one hundred one q可以了"},{"pid":"bd41deca759d0b5c87d8171112697fc455260e5e","tid":971894,"uid":51129,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-07T13:26:20.000Z","msg":"spaced repetition software"},{"pid":"def899f05e43425e65de5bdb63355a633a03ae44","tid":971894,"uid":109655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-07T13:27:53.000Z","msg":"十八廿二都話 如果廿尾打後學語文真係好難 見唔少三四十移民過左十年以上都係講野一舊舊"},{"pid":"5e37c6310a512ddc54a8b54b0caf9303dd85328d","tid":971894,"uid":172441,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-08T03:01:30.000Z","msg":"多啦a夢翻譯蒟蒻幫到你<br />\n簡單快捷方便<br />\n易於儲放不含人造色素防腐劑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95ecaf9be81480c68d41ac32451822173acfaff1","tid":971894,"uid":91833,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-08T03:07:57.000Z","msg":"講咗好多次都冇人理<br />\n專業研究 一個外國人 平均每日講英文兩個鐘<br />\n聽就全日<br />\n當你知道曬所有規則 （grammar + 讀音規則）<br />\n你自己做一個咁嘅環境（ 先係小朋友有聲書＋ 讀兩個鐘）<br />\n乜 語言 都學到啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n講完後次次冇人理，嘥鳩氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我入嚟都係check有咩遊戲出<br />\n之後碌下吹水台<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f176d23f56e11f4578fa7701482d5cc79b13138","tid":971894,"uid":217710,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-09T14:53:14.000Z","msg":"首先係你要中意英文，將你同佢融入（好誇張呀）。本人係聽英文歌培養對英文既興趣。聽都唔夠，要睇歌詞，要唱埋出黎。雖然有啲歌既gramma 唔係好岩，但用一個輕鬆既方法對多啲英文真係可以提升對英文既敏感度。呢個總好過迫自己睇英文書同睇英文書（到你對英文個感覺好啲既時候先再按程度咁睇啦，當然要睇啲你有興既書啦）。"},{"pid":"fd1cdf61aeaf8ae2639d7e156dbcb75318fb2337","tid":971894,"uid":171852,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-10T07:19:13.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e1ef6c7bd10ab42962b4e616efce05c27c6cf186","tid":971894,"uid":212904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-10T18:28:50.000Z","msg":"重刷投胎"},{"pid":"c19643a777318f21245302f889a7ef8177175a03","tid":971894,"uid":44073,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-10T18:41:56.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d73bd8d3d0b1298846f324f5e3d99cb00db00b1e","tid":971894,"uid":171450,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5e37c6310a512ddc54a8b54b0caf9303dd85328d","tid":971894,"uid":172441,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-08T03:01:30.000Z","msg":"多啦a夢翻譯蒟蒻幫到你<br />\n簡單快捷方便<br />\n易於儲放不含人造色素防腐劑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-11T04:38:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 認真問咪派膠<br />\n先唔好講出外國，依家自己英文渣到想搵份好工都唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef84f3455d3c1f7dee3fe6276fe524fe833c2890","tid":971894,"uid":171743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fd1cdf61aeaf8ae2639d7e156dbcb75318fb2337","tid":971894,"uid":171852,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-10T07:19:13.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-15T03:50:22.000Z","msg":"我阿妹有報EF啲課程  我見佢有得24小時用手機學英文  好似好方便咁"},{"pid":"15b4afab5120986092572deeaf01c4f